messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
I need EMS for Officer Matthew.
Can you give me the location again?
Got it, EMS is on their way.
Copy, I need EMS at Holly Tree, no shipyard.
Copy, all shipyard eastbound is blocked off.
352, showing me clear from last.
Copy fire and EMS is on the way.
Wintergreen and Lungleaf Hills with a bag.
Copy, standing by.
I have another bag two houses east.
Copy that.
259, I need any unit stationed at Independence and Shipyard.
Working on that, unit at Independence and Shipyard.
259, switching back to channel three.
Copy that.
We have additional bags on Parkway.
10-4, got the bags on Parkway.
249, transporting two.
I believe they are on Channel 2.
10-4, go to C.
310, go ahead.
